Sleeq replace the physical wallet with a digital wallet which can store all the document you want in one place or several place like in your phone or your computer.
Using this extension you'll find every documents you stored on Sleeq on your computer.

Thanks to Sleeq it is possible to transfer your documents securely and quickly between devices of different platforms.
